</div>

<div class="row case-studies">
	<h4>The results</h4>

	<div class="small-12 medium-12 columns content">
		<p>The demand on the servers far exceeded what was expected. Fortunately, the application was able to bear the load gracefully, and, despite some early hiccups with the payment provider's stability, the campaign was a success. At the time of writing, the campaign has raised more than £2 million, and it continues.</p>
